    v0 = 0.45
    v0 = (tmp * wp.cos(0.78))
    v2 = 0.20
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = (tmp + wp.abs((v2 + 0.04 - v1 + 0.74)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.42)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.93)) + ((tmp + 0.74 - v1 + 0.84) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.19)))
    data[tid] = v0
